{"title":"Nitratos","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Nitratos-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Nitratos","guid":"4umwpL-krwieoxTVw3DlAg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"* Acción rápida y corta duración","guid":"EBjlEXr4fKJX1__LdnUFfQ","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"* ↑ uso: angina aguda, urgencia hipertensiva.","guid":"EoexkYe1rU1-4FJNNAW5uw","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"* Acción prolongada","guid":"wpJlKpTCkSdN7p--SmdsoQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"* ↑ uso: prevención de angina crónica.","guid":"nyVvr-gup9v8Rp4FhrXS3w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Presentación","guid":"h7j2VN-SJS56eZWwgagbdg","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"* Nitroglicerina:","guid":"dpRSBdY7t_ORCMuHIkomHg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"* Comprimidos sublinguales","guid":"RzF5b410JsWQ1mYk-EMFLA","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"* Sublingual: 0.3-0.6 mg cada 5 minutos hasta 3 dosis","guid":"mJVsU8LgdHc9lsIy4MmseQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"* Spray sublingual","guid":"ChkbAqCKuQ_Ih2lS09xpGg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"* Spray: 1-2 pulverizaciones cada 5 minutos hasta 3 dosis","guid":"CkXa9iAhWg3F36ZI9F17wA","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"* Parches transdérmicos","guid":"cttZxp0ynSiP2tlGr10Piw","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"* Parche: 0.2-0. 8 mg/hora","guid":"Vc9Hpo8-CnRAU7GFgts2Rw","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"7","text":"* Solución inyectable","guid":"H5bvQ39ssj6kp1MKXOnh8Q","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"* Inyectable: 5-100 mcg/minuto (dosis inicial)","guid":"dGVfIaKVe7mmO4KjS5QuQg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"6","text":"* Isosorbide dinitrato\\N(ISDN):","guid":"-NnmPz0imndJdskTyuNORw","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"* Comprimidos sublinguales","guid":"CY9FFFiTt5w0EQIRa2hEVg","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"* Sublingual: 2.5-10 mg cada 2-3 horas","guid":"utFiWISRQa4YSzM_FfITPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"* Comprimidos de liberación prolongada","guid":"r8V-OqImxekjpiikye-4BQ","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"* Oral: 10-40 mg cada 6-8 horas","guid":"cfQKzZEyYV8LVhpBjVDhLQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"6","text":"* Isosorbide mononitrato\\N(ISMN):","guid":"_OIdFluU6C91E8ddUwvzLg","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"* Comprimidos","guid":"Y06ix4s8npFPY6UG7PK-_w","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"* Oral: 20 mg dos veces al día","guid":"anqmy1ZLHlUZYfHnYqO5pw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"6","text":"* Nitroprusiato\\Nde sodio:","guid":"Os7Dg0OLSSf9TVQSFS8hfA","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"* Solución inyectable","guid":"vVpdSXvxQqLu0rpwm-2x0A","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"* Inyectable: 0.3-10 mcg/kg/minuto (dosis inicial)","guid":"-Xjfm2j6oFOtoFEB6XFxZw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Mecanismo de\\Nacción","guid":"nvS4Bx_YKFQl2U35DjNDqA","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"⬆ liberación de Óxido Nítrico (NO) → relajación del m. liso vascular → vasodilatación\\N(afecta más a venas ⬆ ⬇ retorno venoso → ⬇ precarga)","guid":"v30emEF_o-yibYkj2a6Duw","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"1. Acción rápida y corta duración","guid":"AcOITn6FDK3EgBCgy8Pb6Q","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"⬆ uso: angina aguda, urgencia hipertensiva.","guid":"y9rOVHlPQ-9wxOdaJ4q-7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"2. Acción prolongada","guid":"EBgiD0RQ5HmjppKYoFdObA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"⬆ uso: prevención de angina crónica.","guid":"VYivhjq3tpzP-HTlGVPhHw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\Nterapéuticos","guid":"ouYxUEd_Sh-mkORNf0EIbg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"⬇ precarga → ⬇ demanda de O2 miocárdica","guid":"k8LYVvGjXRBVIzxUAytJxw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"⬇ trabajo cardíaco","guid":"HfdDlt1OmwrrPfYc9RKcJg","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"⬇ presión arterial","guid":"nmWdXLfoFJIA9krK_WNTqA","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Angina pectoris (tto sintomático).","guid":"YNvvfRbrTfMOz_pRG--AtQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Urgencia hipertensiva.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"• Insuficiencia cardíaca aguda (adjunto).","guid":"5KlStMdgyf9CqoqMxqP9Ow","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"Efectos\\Nsecundarios","guid":"oM2vplAuw9L2IXhj-YlQXQ","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Cefalea inducida por nitratos.","guid":"b55dAmBRI1OsLUc62Uhn2Q","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Reflujo gastroesofágico.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Hipotensión con síncope.","guid":"sbfUGC1axgswttEAomchfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Contraindicaciones/Interacciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Inhibidores de la PDE-5 (⬆ riesgo de hipotensión severa).","guid":"Eb8u87rW9YMmFo73v7kWng","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"Agentes","guid":"qr48C9EApe_l9l5zYT_oBQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Nitratos\\Norgánicos","guid":"YyNg5PEGL4kVufhw8wGwJg","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Nitroglicerina, Isosorbide dinitrato (ISDN), Isosorbide mononitrato (ISMN)","guid":"gt1XOrBjj4bN7b8l6Zv-vg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"⬆ activación por aldehído-reductasa mitocondrial → acción retardada.","guid":"Qo_090TV0jfa-zp-ZIh_og","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"Nitroprusiato\\Nde sodio","guid":"VfPqv-h30d7x5LZgQZJYdw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Activación no enzimática → ⬆ inicio inmediato.","guid":"-RRyR-MVrdBHhvXKloxO2w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"Metabolismo","guid":"ydtDnGNFSzpuwq568FgUOg","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Nitratos orales: ⬆ metabolismo de primer paso hepático.","guid":"7RH0HvNpbtTFLpGg6TGS2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"0","text":"Farmacocinética\\Nde los nitratos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"1. Nitroglicerina","guid":"LrS-vkZiFS3KZF6cn6ym4g","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Oral/sublingual","guid":"U_PgYoMk9rbvotvDM4rHHQ","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"⬆ acción corta: 2-5 min → duración: 15-30 min.","guid":"Zo_yP-uYKmEInD3KN2UH4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Parche transdérmico","guid":"5EWjXDm5Rqo99k34IOVpLQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"⬆ acción larga: inicio: 30 min → duración: 8-14 h.","guid":"ogbgMvjkaHwfSRTHDWtzUQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"56","text":"2. Isosorbide dinitrato\\N(ISDN)","guid":"Gpx5s7vJkfSp9cgRf5G0gQ","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• Sublingual","guid":"fc5pFGD5XcZXv-HSG_m5ew","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"⬆ acción corta: inicio: 2-5 min → duración: 1-2 h.","guid":"HPuO681fzyScENMcIVnk9g","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"• Oral","guid":"5obNnjjr0neXBoTHS52Bhw","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"⬆ acción larga: inicio: 1 h → duración: 4-6 h.","guid":"oxqYkeFSU0a58Ioi3Wtx0Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"56","text":"3. Isosorbide\\Nmononitrato (ISMN)","guid":"JiJbcp8uO5O3B0yWvC9EJw","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Oral","guid":"qw4ETP8rlydlCbip2cJTkw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"⬆ acción larga: inicio: 30-45 min → duración: 6-24 h.","guid":"fA9z6ehMoOlWWUaGsoAsHQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"56","text":"4. Nitroprusiato de sodio","guid":"sr4ACDk1yJQ2SQ6q2m-J9g","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Intravenoso","guid":"ZzvWXwYzuv8fqlx0ecPc1Q","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"⬆ acción corta: inicio inmediato → duración: hasta 1-10 min post infusión.","guid":"LJZQV6ntV0MlPcnOFshCoA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Farmacodinámica\\Nde los Nitratos","guid":"nZgLfYwFz5Fn8Y7IBOcWcw","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"1. Suministro exógeno de\\NÓxido Nítrico (NO)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• NO exógeno → ⬆ guanilil ciclasa → ⬆ GMPc → activación de proteína cinasa G.","guid":"E7Gv7i7Vnnvi8kQtPgxBdg","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"⬆ actividad SERCA → ⬇ Ca²⁺ intracelular → ⬇ reclutamiento de unidades contráctiles → vasodilatación.","guid":"_SwKOipWcSksV7_hMAsVkA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"⬆ actividad de fosfatasa de cadena ligera de miosina → ⬇ miosina fosforilada\\N→ relajación del músculo liso → vasodilatación.","guid":"Dhk-8arMI5u2yBQiJV2aPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"2. Efectos\\Nhemodinámicos","guid":"dV8MxrPkVY6cclZPcgoJWg","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"• ⬇ precarga (dilatación venosa/venous pooling) → ⬇ tensión de la pared miocárdica\\N→ ⬆ perfusión miocárdica.","guid":"wUrxmNbDHrOcUEBIkwjtsQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"• ⬇ postcarga → ⬇ esfuerzo contráctil → ⬇ demanda de O₂ miocárdica.","guid":"8LjEMDKGmmywz9VwLMk72A","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"• Mayor efecto vasodilatador en venas que arterias\\N(excepto nitroprusiato de sodio).","guid":"_wVJIyXYxnDHFHoaOmKlzA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"• Dilatación coronaria → ⬆ perfusión miocárdica.","guid":"I_1Ck0NVe0i59Wc3BDitgA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"• En pacientes con CAD aterosclerótica: arteriolas ya dilatadas (por estenosis limitante del flujo)\\N→ ⬇ efecto adicional de los nitratos sobre dilatación coronaria.","guid":"OSSTVM2TnwnPx8eRFKRTQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"73","text":"3. Alivio del\\Ndolor anginoso","guid":"EC7z-AAhM4yNKKitI8M0Ig","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• ⬇ precarga (dilatación venosa) →\\N⬇ tamaño cardíaco → ⬇ demanda\\Nde O₂ → ⬇ dolor.","guid":"G2E64M9Xvlb_o3ErUyn9TQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"Efectos adversos\\Nde los nitratos","guid":"hjShCnf3yk45bnRdQ3OCJA","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"1. Disregulación\\Ncirculatoria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Hipotensión → actividad simpática refleja → taquicardia refleja → síncope por nitratos.","guid":"ej4SfK_SFEA_zlxHsBz51Q","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"• Uso de β-bloqueadores para contrarrestar.","guid":"5QektKga50Jed2UzZrwfhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"2. Cefalea inducida por nitratos","guid":"aFR2UkIA-PR0PkIK5R6DQw","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• Dilatación de arterias cerebrales → cefalea.","guid":"4P1pwlsrh0LkYfALZ54D0Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"86","text":"3. Rubor facial","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Vasodilatación periférica → flushing.","guid":"5vOBMmGuUJN1jrnfmk3Jkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"86","text":"4. Reflujo gastroesofágico","guid":"1fFBs2L7sFtH9GpVk3GFBw","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• Relajación del esfínter esofágico inferior → reflujo gastroesofágico.","guid":"1xSAU8lS0hNqeJIx3r_JtA","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"86","text":"5. Desarrollo de tolerancia","guid":"0eZniYgpumHy4RO65Az2rg","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Prevención: terapia intermitente con intervalos libres de nitratos de al menos 8 h.","guid":"tGaxYYB2xvS8g-01f6bJkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"86","text":"6. Toxicidad por cianuro","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Tras infusión de nitroprusiato de sodio → ver intoxicación por cianuro.","guid":"BhgO0aS31oWvc89bDgrkDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"86","text":"7. Metahemoglobinemia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Oxidación de hierro en hemoglobina → ⬆ methemoglobina → metahemoglobinemia.","guid":"7MeAjXx4k9CTxq_6MOMCPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"86","text":"8. “Enfermedad\\Ndel lunes”","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"Fertilizante de césped ","guid":"1SVOgZohq1gyJaG_b2djbg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• Trabajadores expuestos a nitratos desarrollan tolerancia durante la semana laboral.","guid":"Ru02ZXOUeHy_yMS-idHXDA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"• No exposición durante los fines de semana → pérdida de tolerancia.","guid":"-nYzJlwPWw970kuqj6CUJw","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"• Reexposición el lunes → mareo, taquicardia y cefalea.","guid":"FNatVcLZZwB39Fk2hR7fwA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones de\\Nlos nitratos","guid":"0_LLlqvj412k_rdtgNgkgg","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"1. Angina pectoris","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Nitratos de acción corta","guid":"D6Gx4GDx8qDYKDJtAL4OBw","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"• Nitroglicerina sublingual, dinitrato de isosorbide o spray de nitroglicerina\\N→ tto de ataques agudos.","guid":"s9ShFOP-XMhQ9Wu_okPYvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• Nitratos de acción\\Nprolongada","guid":"6y6KDM4u45nV6l7cojCJ8A","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Mononitrato de isosorbide (2-3 veces/día) → profilaxis anginal.","guid":"oD4K8sTXocVJuxgTaCQYmQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"• No sufre metabolismo de primer paso hepático → ⬆ biodisponibilidad (~100%).","guid":"RaqUMYpiUhM2CVWBxngZ0Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"107","text":"2. Crisis hipertensiva","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"• Reducción rápida y a corto plazo de la presión arterial.","guid":"EeVDHfqHzrRq-2-4V4h_aQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"107","text":"3. Síndrome coronario agudo","guid":"bmUI3Wr2khzK-O0QilAbLg","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"• Mejora la perfusión miocárdica y ⬇ demanda de O₂.","guid":"pimIaccOBK39MXQbW8XOHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"107","text":"4. Edema pulmonar hipertensivo","guid":"CUii_hYT7GamNruq3rhQ3Q","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Vasodilatación → ⬇ presión en la vasculatura pulmonar.","guid":"fBejdeznhKBGx469VqpUYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"107","text":"5. Insuficiencia cardíaca crónica","guid":"cyW6eJqfeq1rahjCnFuDnA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"• Mejora la función cardíaca al ⬇ precarga y postcarga.","guid":"WpcCcjgUkGvqoIf0_fCAoA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"0","text":"Contraindicaciones\\Nde los nitratos","guid":"2Q3Q1Fnhf5DCvemmL1rz1A","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"1. Hipotensión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"• Riesgo de hipotensión severa si se toma dentro de 24 h de un inhibidor de PDE-5\\N(ej. pacientes con angina pectoris).","guid":"V_0ex23ggnXYKOkpclfpvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"2. Estenosis del tracto de salida\\Ndel ventrículo izquierdo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Ej. estenosis aórtica, miocardiopatía hipertrófica\\N→ ⬆ riesgo de colapso hemodinámico.","guid":"Viav8c4wondYKSm1O0IWLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"122","text":"3. Infarto de miocardio con\\Ninsuficiencia del ventrículo derecho","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"• Vasodilatación excesiva\\N→ ⬇ perfusión coronaria derecha.","guid":"_Y_tW94OZcWQXXGQD1cChQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"122","text":"4. ⬆ Presión intracraneal","guid":"b0W7PSx9K9AEWbykzxmnwA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• ⬆ riesgo de herniación cerebral por vasodilatación.","guid":"G12EE6BXnuIWjk1q3ynXyA","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":130,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Nitratos-2024","id":"map_315","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Nitratos-2024"}